title: The Suicide Tunnel
description: In 2017, two boys discover and enter a tunnel in the woods near their town. When the boys don’t return, the townspeople begin a search for them and come across the tunnel, but everyone who has gone in has never come out. Nicknaming it “the Suicide Tunnel”, the government fences in the area and takes control of studying it. A few years later, four high-school students who are sick of their lives decide to take the ultimate risk and enter the Suicide Tunnel together. What will they find and will they ever return?
author: A.S. Tabitha
